I'll come to you
for a five-day luxury tour then.

159
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:22,919
- Fine. I'm worried that you won't come.
- Go ahead. I'll leave it here.

160
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:24,420
- Bye.
- Bye.

161
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:26,480
- Goodbye.
- Go on, goodbye.

162
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,339
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

163
00:15:27,339 --> 00:15:29,240
- Come to see us when you have time.
- Okay.

164
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,380
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

165
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:33,579
- Goodbye.
- Remember to call me.

166
00:15:34,939 --> 00:15:35,660
Don't forget the gifts.

167
00:15:47,619 --> 00:15:49,380
Boss, you're so emotional.

168
00:15:51,140 --> 00:15:52,420
