171
00:16:04,819 --> 00:16:05,420
Let's go.

172
00:16:16,052 --> 00:16:19,792
(Girl's Dorm Building 3)

173
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:32,660
It really feels like a dream.

174
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:40,600
Yeah, I finally understand why
