If possible,)

194
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:39,339
(I hope we can collaborate,
not as harmonies but as a duet.)

195
00:18:47,619 --> 00:18:48,179
Sheng.

196
00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:51,099
Sheng.

197
